   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "cm"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_y\">語録</span>\n国をあやまる第一線の政治家が三人いる、それは<a href=\"../p/myosuke.html\">松岡洋右</a>、<a href=\"../p/kfumimar.html\">近衛文麿</a>、<a href=\"../p/hkiiciro.html\">平沼騏一郎</a>だ。\n"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "tx"
   },
   "html": "\n<div><span class=\"m_b\">引用</span>純忠一途の古武士的硬骨漢で、<a href=\"../1940/yona_1.html\">米内内閣</a>の生みの親であった。</div>\n<div class=\"txr\"><a href=\"../text/tm2saion.html\">豊田穣 「西園寺公望（下）」</a>\n　Ｐ．３７３<span class=\"book\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%259C%2592%25E5%25AF%25BA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%259B%25E2%2580%2595%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%25E3%2581%25AE%25E5%2585%2583%25E8%2580%2581%2520%2528%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%25B7%25BB%2529%2520\" target=\"_blank\">この本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></span></div>\n"
  },
